OL,3,CHeadteacher admits attacking fellow
OL,4,Cteacher at his secondary school
OL,6,FA headteacher has admitted attacking a
OL,7,Ffellow teacher at his secondary school.
OL,9,FPolice were called to St Joseph's
OL,10,FCatholic School and Sixth Form Centre
OL,11,Fin Aberavon, Port Talbot on 5 March
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of an assault.
OL,14,F54-year-old Anthony Felton appeared at
OL,15,FSwansea Crown Court today and pleaded
OL,16,Fguilty to attempted grievous bodily
OL,17,Fharm with intent against Richard Pyke,
OL,18,F51.
