OL,3,CHeadteacher admits attacking fellow
OL,4,Cteacher at his secondary school
OL,6,FFollowing the incident police said Mr
OL,7,FPyke had been discharged from hospital
OL,8,Fafter suffering minor injuries.
OL,10,FFelton spoke only to confirm his name
OL,11,Fand enter his pleas as he appeared by
OL,12,Fvideo-link from prison.
OL,14,FThe court heard how Felton inflicted
OL,15,F"a number of blows" to Mr Pyke, which
OL,16,Fhad all been caught on CCTV.
OL,18,FJudge Paul Thomas KC said the offence
OL,19,Fwas serious enough to warrant a prison
OL,20,Fsentence.
