OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Archdiocese
OL,7,Fsaid: "We appreciate that this is a
OL,8,Fdifficult time for the school, and our
OL,9,Fthoughts and prayers are especially
OL,10,Fwith the school community.
OL,12,F"The education department of the
OL,13,FArchdiocese of Cardiff-Menevia is
OL,14,Fworking with the governors, the school
OL,15,Fand the local authority to ensure that
OL,16,Fthe necessary support is in place.
OL,18,F"We ask the Catholic community in the
OL,19,FArchdiocese to remember all affected
OL,20,Fby these events in their prayers".
